    "Robotic operation Automation (RPA) has the potential to improve the efficiency and profitability of this particular operation.",
    "Credit card business volumeBased on the 2020 annual report of Mingsheng Banks, the total number of credit cards issued by the bank stands at 61.67 million.",
    "In the year 2020, the quantity of newly issued credit cards amounted to 4.21 million.",
    "Approximately 70% of newly issued credit cards are obtained by in-person applications at the front desk, while the remaining percentage is acquired using internet platforms or mobile devices.",
    "In the year 2020, a total of around 2.95 million credit cards were issued using manual processes."
